        <p>This platform addresses the pressing need for personalized guidance, enabling mentees to navigate their career paths effectively. By facilitating connections based on mentor availability and expertise, "Guiding Guru" empowers users to seek advice on critical topics such as career development, skill enhancement, and industry insights.</p>

